<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM3.3">
<l>ellē yīteṉṉa viḷamai yemmaṉai mārkāṇi loṭṭār</l>
<l>pollāṅ kīteṉṟu karutāy pūṅkurun tēṟi yirutti</l>
<l>villā lilaṅkai yaḻittāy nīvēṇṭiya tellān taruvōm</l>
<l>pallārum kāṇāmē pōvōm paṭṭaip paṇittaru ḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Here, you! What is this childishness? If our mothers see [this], they will not allow [us home].</l>
<l>You will not consider this as wickedness! O You destroyed Laṅkā with a bow!</l>
<l>Climbing a flowering sweet lime tree, You are sitting [upon it].</l>
<l>We will give [You] all You want! We will leave without many people seeing [us].</l>
<l rend="indent">Do grace to give [back our] silk clothes!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
